---
import "../../styles/main.css"
import Nav from "../../components/Nav.astro"
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro"
import ThemeInit from "../../components/ThemeInit.astro"
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <ThemeInit />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Learning Stories - Inspiring Tales of Famous Learners | FluentCards</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Inspiring stories of famous figures who mastered learning through repetition, deliberate practice, and perseverance. From Frederick Douglass to Warren Buffett." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://fluentcards.org/stories/" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Learning Stories - FluentCards" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Inspiring stories of famous learners and the power of repetition." />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://fluentcards.org/stories/" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "CollectionPage", "name": "Learning Stories", "url": "https://fluentcards.org/stories/" }
  </script>
  <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-4482389932723468" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body class="font-sans text-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark dark:text-slate-400 antialiased overflow-x-hidden transition-colors duration-300">
<Nav currentPath="/stories/" />

<section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6 text-center">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto reveal-up">
    <span class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/20 to-teal-400/20 text-primary px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4 border border-primary/20">Inspiring Stories</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Learning Stories</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Tales of remarkable individuals who mastered their craft through repetition, deliberate practice, and unwavering determination. Their journeys prove that learning is a skill anyone can develop.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pb-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">

      <a href="/stories/frederick-douglass-reading/" class="group bg-white dark:bg-surface-card rounded-xl border-2 border-primary/20 dark:border-emerald-900/40 p-6 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 reveal-pop relative">
        <span class="absolute -top-2.5 -right-2.5 bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">New</span>
        <span class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-3 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4">Stories</span>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2 leading-snug group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Frederick Douglass: How a Slave Taught Himself to Read and Changed History</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4 line-clamp-3">How an enslaved child taught himself to read against every obstacle, proving that the desire to learn can overcome any barrier.</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-semibold">13 min read</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/stories/benjamin-franklin-self-education/" class="group bg-white dark:bg-surface-card rounded-xl border-2 border-primary/20 dark:border-emerald-900/40 p-6 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 reveal-pop delay-1 relative">
        <span class="absolute -top-2.5 -right-2.5 bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">New</span>
        <span class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-3 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4">Stories</span>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2 leading-snug group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Benjamin Franklin's Self-Education: The Blueprint for Lifelong Learning</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4 line-clamp-3">How a school dropout taught himself to write at a world-class level through deliberate practice and systematic self-improvement.</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-semibold">12 min read</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/stories/warren-buffett-reading-habit/" class="group bg-white dark:bg-surface-card rounded-xl border-2 border-primary/20 dark:border-emerald-900/40 p-6 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 reveal-pop delay-2 relative">
        <span class="absolute -top-2.5 -right-2.5 bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">New</span>
        <span class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-3 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4">Stories</span>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2 leading-snug group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Warren Buffett's Reading Habit: How 500 Pages a Day Built a Fortune</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4 line-clamp-3">How five to six hours of daily reading built the knowledge that made Buffett the world's greatest investor.</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-semibold">12 min read</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/stories/kato-lomb-polyglot-secrets/" class="group bg-white dark:bg-surface-card rounded-xl border-2 border-primary/20 dark:border-emerald-900/40 p-6 hover:border-primary hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 reveal-pop delay-3 relative">
        <span class="absolute -top-2.5 -right-2.5 bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">New</span>
        <span class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-3 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4">Stories</span>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2 leading-snug group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Kato Lomb: The Hungarian Polyglot Who Mastered 16 Languages</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4 line-clamp-3">How a chemist with no language talent learned 16 languages through massive reading and context-based learning.</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-semibold">14 min read</span>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<Footer />
<script>const o=new IntersectionObserver(e=>{e.forEach(e=>{e.isIntersecting&&e.target.classList.add("visible")})},{threshold:.08});document.querySelectorAll(".reveal-up, .reveal-pop").forEach(e=>o.observe(e));</script>
</body>
</html>
